pageTitle: Your grant information is not available
h1: Your grant information is not available
p1: You cannot start a claim because your grant information is not available.

ul.li1: you have registered for an online claims account within the past 24 hours
ul.li2: there was an issue creating your online account or we do not have all the correct details

p3: Wait at least 24 hours after you register for an online claims account, and check back again.
link1: If your grant information is still not available, contact Access to Work.
